{"tid":1611273,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣外交一齊救！] 香港人！到我地stand with台灣喇, 入黎簽爆佢","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:28:24.000Z","uid":36716,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be237117c7376d7d947db540265a31882b11ded9","tid":1611273,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">實現we connect</span></strong></span><br />\n台灣支持左我地好耐,到我地支持佢地<br />\n<br />\n德國國會請願連署<br />\n<br />\n最近有德國民眾向德國國會提出請願案「<strong>Petition 95643</strong>」，要求德國政府承認台灣，並與中華民國（台灣）建交。這個請願案需要在10月9日為止達到50,000人連署才能成案，並約束德國政府針對連署內容回應。目前已經有33,108人連署。最重要的是，連署人<strong>並不需要是德國人，任何國籍的民眾都可以參與連署。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的確係幾複雜<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">台灣既新聞同教學網站</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://talk.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2926199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalk.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2926199&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ec7c17a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalk.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2926199&h=9d6fdd5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://talk.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2926199</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聯署link</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_05%2F_31%2FPetition_95643.mitzeichnen.html&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=98a56c97\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html</a>"},{"pid":"679b4d6ad138b1254c876fe52435e8d18c67f574","tid":1611273,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl